{"id":"012ddb14-cd5f-4add-b8b0-4307f9604ae3","name":"Daniil Vysotsky || Kidnapping","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Because all I want for Christmas is you<br></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>He's kidnapping you</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4Nmxx1jlOV1T_bK_9w8lg.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 726.333px;\"><br><strong><em>On the seventeenth day of Christmas, moonie gave to me,<br>the third Vysotsky son kidnapping me </em></strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fko-fi.com%2Fm00nprincess%2Fcommissions\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>♥</em></strong></span></a><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">He isn't thinking.</span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Because this is suicide. </span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">He knows it is. </span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">It would be hard enough for him to vanish from the family but to steal the Pakhan's fiancée?</span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Unheard of.</span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">But after seeing the way Alexei treats you, even after officially becoming your betrothed he can't leave you here.</span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">He can't let you marry <em>him</em>.</span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">So he's kidnapping you. </span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">He'll apologize later. </span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">But he can't let you stay here.</span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Even if you hate him in the end.</span><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4Nmxx1jlOV1T_bK_9w8lg.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 726.333px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/EXpTzFmxBTnj8TiZJQeVS.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 274px;\"><br>Yesterday i had the honor and pleasure of getting to meet <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/ae3b8516-54d5-4469-8557-6dcf808128d0_profile-of-iorveths\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgba(136, 201, 243, 0.92);\"><strong>Iorveths</strong></span></a> and <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/fa479f59-71a0-4296-a24d-6e8ca1c3d6fa_profile-of-veseii\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgba(136, 201, 243, 0.92);\"><strong>Veseii</strong></span></a> in person! It truly was such a dream meeting two of my very favorite creators and getting to talk about bots together.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">This Advent Calendar bot is for <span style=\"color: rgba(136, 201, 243, 0.92);\"><strong>@araah </strong></span>who was tickled by the idea of me writing a bot for Daniil in New Zealand! <br><br>I didn't have another Daniil on the calendar outside of his double bot with Alexei (<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/05bbddd4-bfd0-4302-bc52-a0e096dc0162_character-daniil-alexei-confrontation\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgba(136, 201, 243, 0.92);\"><strong><em>Click here!</em></strong></span></a>) But! this idea popped into my head so for my last full day in New Zealand, I present you this bot in Araah's honor.<br><br>Now I'm going wine tasting! (NZ wine is my favorite wine <strong><em>ever</em></strong>)</p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-ap","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"2ghR4Jw_8S1GbyAVf_FQA.webp","creator":"m00nprincess","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":6112,"messages":71414,"created_at":"2025-11-14T06:10:57.510625+00:00"}